      "text_block": {
        "title": "门口来了关羽",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f1_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "一个推独轮车的大汉闯进村店，只想痛饮一碗，马上进城投军。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f1_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "刘备一眼看出，这不是路人，这是能在乱世里站住的人。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.0,
        "w": 1.0,
        "h": 0.2204
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f2",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p03_s1",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p03-page-01-f2",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "三人认出彼此",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f2_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "关羽只报了几句：他来自河东，杀过欺人的豪强，已经逃亡多年。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f2_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "刘备说出讨贼安民的志向后，张飞和关羽都明白，三个人要走同一条路。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.2204,
        "w": 0.4973,
        "h": 0.186
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f3",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p03_s2",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p03-page-01-f3",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "张飞提出结义",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f3_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "张飞把两人带到庄后桃园。花开正盛，他第一次收起玩笑。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f3_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "他提议祭告天地，结为兄弟，把这条命先绑在一起。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.4973,
        "y": 0.2204,
        "w": 0.5027,
        "h": 0.186
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f4",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p03_s2",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p03-page-01-f4",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "桃园之誓",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f4_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "次日，三人在桃花下焚香跪拜。刘备为兄，关羽次之，张飞为弟。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f4_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "他们发誓同心协力，救人危难；不求同生，但求同死。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.4064,
        "w": 1.0,
        "h": 0.1842
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f5",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p03_s3",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p03-page-01-f5",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "起兵的本钱到了",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f5_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "刚结义，他们就撞上现实：有志气，却没有马，也没有钱铁。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f5_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "两位北方马商折返路过，听完刘备的志向，留下五十匹马、金银和镔铁。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.5906,
        "w": 0.4909,
        "h": 0.1794
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f6",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p03_s3",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p03-page-01-f6",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "一支队伍成形",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f6_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "有了马和铁，三兄弟各得兵器，披上铠甲，又聚起五百多名乡勇。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f6_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "刘备执双股剑，关羽提青龙刀，张飞横丈八矛，这才像真正上路的人。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.4909,
        "y": 0.5906,
        "w": 0.5091,
        "h": 0.1794
      }
